# VibeTrade Project Structure
## Overview
VibeTrade is a Next.js application built with modern web technologies for AI agent trading on Sui blockchain.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js (App Router)
- **Styling**: TailwindCSS
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui
- **Theme**: Dark/Light mode with next-themes
- **Icons**: Lucide React

## Directory Structure
```
src/
├── app/
│   ├── layout.js        # Root layout with ThemeProvider
│   └── page.js          # Home page
├── components/
│   ├── ui/              # shadcn/ui components
│   │   ├── button.jsx
│   │   ├── card.jsx
│   │   ├── dialog.jsx
│   │   ├── form.jsx
│   │   ├── input.jsx
│   │   ├── label.jsx
│   │   └── sidebar.jsx
│   ├── app-sidebar.jsx  # Main application sidebar
│   ├── nav-projects.jsx # Projects navigation
│   ├── nav-secondary.jsx # Secondary navigation
│   ├── nav-user.jsx     # User navigation component
│   └── theme-toggle.jsx # Theme switcher component
```

## Key Components

### AppSidebar
The main sidebar component that includes:
- Logo/Brand header
- Project navigation
- Secondary navigation (Support, Docs)
- Theme toggle
- User profile section

### Navigation Components
- **NavProjects**: Handles project navigation (Chat, Tokens, Wallet)
- **NavSecondary**: Secondary navigation items (Support, Docs)
- **NavUser**: User profile section
- **ThemeToggle**: Dark/Light mode switcher

### Theme System
- Uses `next-themes` for theme management
- Supports light/dark modes
- System theme detection
- Smooth theme transitions

## Styling
- TailwindCSS for utility-first styling
- Custom sidebar styling with shadcn/ui
- Responsive design
- Dark mode support with CSS variables

